Esiaai e Paulo te Sesalonike


1  Amu iyiololo intae maate, ilalashera inchere ime ene pesho elotunoto ang nikietuo enitii intae. 
2   Amu iyiololo, enkisilisiloto o morot nikinoto te Filipi, neme toki amu eishoo iyiook Enkai empijan nikilikinye intae Ilomon Supati, hoo netii kesha sapuk. 
3  Amu ore esayiakinoto ang nemepuku eing'uaa enkitapong'oroto anaa ilduruki neme to losek eitobiruaki. 
4  Kake ore anaa enatonyorrayie iyiook Enkai neisiligaki too Lomon Supati, neijia kijo iyiook neme pee kintiship iltung'ana, kake pee kintiship Enkai naineneng iltauja lang. 
5  Amu ore iyiook neitu ae kata kiaasishore irorei le nkilelemare, anaa eniyiololo, aashu kiaata imbaa naisudoo eului, naa Enkai shakeni; 
6  neitu king'oru enkisisa too ltung'ana, aa te intae, arashu te kulikae, hoo naa anaata kinkuna neijia anaa ilkipaareta le Kristo. 
7  Kake aikibor apa ti atua intae anaa enkaibung'ani naing'or inkera enyena. 
8  Neaku ore te nkaripo kiyieu intae kiterretenate pee king'ar te nebo intae neme ilomon ake Supati maate, kake oyiook sii maate amu itaa intae kiroteti oleng te iyiook.


9  Amu idamumu intae enyamali ang o esiaai nagol, ilalashera, kitaasishote dama o kewarie, pee mikiek hoo likae te intae, kiliki intae Ilomon Supati le Nkai. 
10  Irara intae shakeni, naa neijia sii etiu Enkai, te sinyatisho o te supatisho nimikiaata entiyoto to lkuaak lang ti alo intae ilairukok. 
11  Iyiololo aajo kintaasa intae anaa enaitaas menye inkera enyena, kinkoo pooki ng'ae te intae nikintagol oshuaa, nikintanapa intae. 
12  Pee ipuopuo te nkishon naishiaakino te Nkai, ilo oipotoki intae atua enkitoria enye makewan e nkitoo.


13  Nikincho sii iyiook oshiaake Enkai enashe te nkaraki ena, inchere pee ing'amumu ororei le Enkai litoning'o te iyiook, eitu intae ing'amumu anaa ororei loo ltung'ana, kake anaa enatiu te dede orerei le Enkai ti atua intae ilairukok. 
14   Amu ore intae loo lalashera intoduaarie ate isirito e Enkai ti atua Kristo Yesu naatii atua Yudea. Amu inoto sii intae olosilisili too ltung'ana lo lorere linyi anaa enanoto sii ninche too Lyahudi, 
15   laa ninche ootaara ndung'ot pokira metuata Olaitoriani Yesu o loibonok le Nkai, nearaa iyiook ong'ata, nemeitiship Enkai neibooyo ltung'ana pooki 
16  emitiki iyiook kiliki Loreren enaiko pee eitajeuni, ejo pee etum aaiputu emborei o ng'ok enye pooki. Kake eewuo engoro e Enkai te nkiting'oto shumata ninche.

Eyieunoto e Paulo pee emutan ninche aigil


17  Kake ore ilalashera anaa neorieki iyiook intae te nkiti kata, too seseni neme too ltauja, kitoinyua o te yieuna sapuk o te nyorrata kitok pee kiduaa inkomomi. 
18  Amu kitayieutua nikiponu enitii intae, atetema nanu Paulo enkata neme nabo kake eibooyie iyiook shetani. 
19  Amu ainyoo osiligi lang aashu eng'ida aashu entoki naisul nikiwuasare te dukuya Olaitoriani lang Yesu te lotunoto enye? Aime intae? 
20  Amu irara intae enkitoo ang o eng'ida ang.

